      "Text": "Security update for lcms2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for lcms2 fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-41254: integer overflow in CubeSize in cmslut.c (bsc#1264994).\n- CVE-2026-42798: integer overflow in ParseCube in cmscgats.c (bsc#1263703).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
